snippet.title: Enigma of Fear | Release Date Teaser
snippet.description:
“In a place that doesn’t exist, young detective Mia and her little dog Lupi investigate the disappearance of her father, one of the most skilled agents in the world and the leader of Ordo Realitas, an organization of paranormal detectives. Enigma of Fear is a game of investigation and mystery in Pixel Art/3D where your deduction is your guide.

#steamgame #enigmaoffear #ordemparanormal #cellbit #dumativa

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1507580
Pre-Order: https:/nuuvem.com/fear

Developed by Cellbit and Dumativa 
Published by: Nuuvem
Release Date: November 28th 2024
